<headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 13 at 2:56AM EDT  by NWS New York City - Upton</headline>
<description>...LOCALLY DENSE FOG ACROSS LONG ISLAND AND COASTAL CONNECTICUT...
Widespread fog has reduced visibilities below a mile across Long
Island and the Connecticut coast, with locally dense fog reducing
visibilities to 1/4 mile. If traveling use caution. Allow for
extra room between you and the vehicle in front of you and use fog
lights if available.</description>
